How To Install:
---------------

1. Install package itools from repository
   $ sudo apt-get install itools

2. Create .iprayrc based on your location
   $ touch ~/.iprayrc
   $ nano ~/.iprayrc

3. Fill it with your information, e.g: city, latitude, longitude
   Example:
	City: Jakarta
	Latitude: -5.7759361
	Longitude: 106.1174513
	UTC: 7
	AngleMethod: 1
	Mathhab: 1

4. For more information about .ipraytime, please see the manual:
   $ man ipraytime

5. Extract all the file from the archive into ~/.conky

6. Run conky with:
   $ conky --c ~/.conky/conkyrc
